Package org.dspace.app.oai

Class Summary
DIDLCrosswalk DSpace Item DIDL crosswalk.
DSpaceOAICatalog This is class extends OAICat's AbstractCatalog base class to allow metadata harvesting of the metadata in DSpace via OAI-PMH 2.0.
DSpaceRecordFactory Implementation of the OAICat RecordFactory base class for DSpace items.
LoadDSpaceOAIConfig Deprecated. Use Servlet Context Listener provided in dspace-api (remove in > 1.5.x)
METSCrosswalk OAICat crosswalk to allow METS to be harvested.
OAIDCCrosswalk OAI_DC Crosswalk implementation based on oaidc.properties file.
PluginCrosswalk An OAICat Crosswalk implementation that calls, in turn, on DisseminationCrosswalk plugins.
RDFCrosswalk An OAICat Crosswalk implementation that extracts DSpace items into typed RDF format.
UKETDDCCrosswalk A Crosswalk implementation that extracts qualified Dublin Core from DSpace items into the uketd_dc format.
